To compile, one needs ocaml 4.02. Right now the simplest way to install it is through
  opam switch 4.02.0+trunk
  opam install ocamlfind

To switch back to your previous ocaml, you can type
  opam switch
to see the list of installed compilers.

Many thanks to http://whitequark.org/blog/2014/04/16/a-guide-to-extension-points-in-ocaml/